### Login as admin user (required for API access)
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin

### Get all expenses (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses

### Get expense by ID (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/1

### Create new expense - Lunch (requires login session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Lunch",
  "amount": 12.50,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2024-12-19"
}

### Create new expense - Coffee (requires login session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Coffee",
  "amount": 5.00,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2024-12-19"
}

### Create new expense - Bus ticket (requires login session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Bus ticket",
  "amount": 3.50,
  "category": "Transport",
  "date": "2024-12-19"
}

### Create expense with invalid category (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Invalid test",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "category": "InvalidCategory",
  "date": "2024-12-19"
}

### Get expenses by category - Food (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/category/Food

### Get expenses by category - Transport (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/category/Transport

### Delete expense by ID (requires login session)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/1

### Delete all expenses (requires login session)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/expenses

### Get total amount of all expenses (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/total

### Add random expense (requires login session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/random

### Add multiple random expenses (requires login session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/random/5

### Filter expenses by category using query parameter - Food (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=Food

### Filter expenses by category using query parameter - Transport (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=Transport

### Filter expenses by category - case insensitive (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=food

### Filter expenses by non-existing category (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=Travel

### Filter expenses with empty category - should return all (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=

### Filter expenses with whitespace category (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=  Food  

### Sort expenses by amount (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?sortBy=amount

### Sort expenses by date (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?sortBy=date

### Sort expenses by description (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?sortBy=description

### Filter and sort combined (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses?category=Food&sortBy=amount

### Filter by date range (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/filter?startDate=2024-12-01&endDate=2024-12-31

### Get paginated expenses (requires login session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/page?page=0&size=5

### Test unauthorized access (without login) - should return 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses

